  '["As a child,\nI vaguely dreamed of becoming someone who changes the world.","While pondering how to change the world,\nthe answer that found me was ''software''.","Something that can reach everyone equally,\nregardless of environment or conditions.","Something that can be provided for free, anytime, anywhere,\ntransforming into countless forms beside the user\nto help their lives.","I was captivated by that infinite possibility.","And so, starting from high school,\nI began my voyage toward the dream of being a ''world-changing developer''.","To you who opened my voyage''s suitcase today,\nI''d like to play you my most cherished songs."]'
